dct_title_s: Abbildung der Keÿs[rl] Freyen-Reichs-Wahl-und-Handelstatt Franckfurt am Mayn : mit ihrem Gebiet und Gräntzen
dct_description_sm: Covers Frankfurt am Main and surrounding environs; relief shown pictorially and by hachures. Appears in: Novus atlas C. tabularum ... Nürnberg : excusus in officina Homanniana, 1731-[1737?]. Above upper margin: "Cum Privilegio Sac. Cæs. Majestatis". Includes legend. Below map: view and 2 ill. engravings in historiated title-cartouches.
dct_subject_sm: Frankfurt am Main (Germany)—Aerial views—Early works to 1800
